  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Friendly Droppets</i></strong><i> </i>is a simple physics based puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/17d5aa10d6aa7acc7edad0eedf4cba27.webp?t=1740609904\" width=159 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/80a49b9c78ce518889a0d09f945e2274.poster.avif?t=1740609904\" width=220 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/80a49b9c78ce518889a0d09f945e2274.webm?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/80a49b9c78ce518889a0d09f945e2274.mp4?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time.<br>Rotate and position the <strong>Droppet</strong> and let it fall on the <strong>Panda</strong>'s head.<br>Try to collect the special item in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill the gauge to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/241e87560123eb092ac672a425cc4d88.poster.avif?t=1740609904\" width=146 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/241e87560123eb092ac672a425cc4d88.webm?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/241e87560123eb092ac672a425cc4d88.mp4?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/5a692cce076ce515f7967665308e5b57.webp?t=1740609904\" width=163 height=25 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pile and organize <strong>Droppets</strong> in 120 Levels;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience 12 Worlds with increasingly challenging <strong>Panda</strong> hats and movements<br>(you can play <strong>the first 10 worlds, </strong>they are unlocked at the start on the Level Select screen);</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 15 types of object;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the way you want (open the Option Screen on the main menu):</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/be27c578fa444a7fe17d44250f67162e.avif?t=1740609904\" width=87 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CASUAL</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For a relaxed gameplay;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slower <strong>Panda</strong> movements;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easier to fill gauge.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/0597a4c01d1081e74db87828a81c6486.avif?t=1740609904\" width=87 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHALLENGE</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For more experienced players;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Faster <strong>Panda</strong> movements;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gauge requires more <strong>Droppets</strong> to fill;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A counter appears on the bottom right corner (no incidence on the game play).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/cb33aefee5a81266babc35bbda3dd7fc.webp?t=1740609904\" width=78 height=31 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can rotate the <strong>Droppet</strong> freely or by 45 degrees increments.<br>The closer the <strong>Droppet</strong>'s angle is to its landing surface's angle,<br>the less of a bounce will follow its landing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Placing too many <strong>Droppets</strong> directly on top of a single one<br>can push that <strong>Droppet</strong> out of the pile.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Panda</strong> in the first levels of each world has no hat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to collect the object 3 times on <strong>Casual</strong> mode and only once in <strong>Challenge</strong> mode<br>to add it to your collection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill a collection page to unlock an <strong>Achievement</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take your time.</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Friendly Droppets</i></strong><i> </i>is a simple physics based puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/17d5aa10d6aa7acc7edad0eedf4cba27.webp?t=1740609904\" width=159 height=26 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/80a49b9c78ce518889a0d09f945e2274.poster.avif?t=1740609904\" width=220 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/80a49b9c78ce518889a0d09f945e2274.webm?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/80a49b9c78ce518889a0d09f945e2274.mp4?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time.<br>Rotate and position the <strong>Droppet</strong> and let it fall on the <strong>Panda</strong>'s head.<br>Try to collect the special item in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill the gauge to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/241e87560123eb092ac672a425cc4d88.poster.avif?t=1740609904\" width=146 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/241e87560123eb092ac672a425cc4d88.webm?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/241e87560123eb092ac672a425cc4d88.mp4?t=1740609904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragra