the game play).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348720/extras/cb33aefee5a81266babc35bbda3dd7fc.webp?t=1740609904\" width=78 height=31 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can rotate the <strong>Droppet</strong> freely or by 45 degrees increments.<br>The closer the <strong>Droppet</strong>'s angle is to its landing surface's angle,<br>the less of a bounce will follow its landing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Placing too many <strong>Droppets</strong> directly on top of a single one<br>can push that <strong>Droppet</strong> out of the pile.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Panda</strong> in the first levels of each world has no hat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to collect the object 3 times on <strong>Casual</strong> mode and only once in <strong>Challenge</strong> mode<br>to add it to your collection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill a collection page to unlock an <strong>Achievement</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take your time.</strong></p></li></ul>",
